      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Welcome to Global Dynamics! As part of your onboarding, we'll be introducing you to our \"Workplace Etiquette 101\" training module. This guide will help you understand the expectations and standards we uphold at our company. Key concepts include demonstrating **respect** for your colleagues and clients, understanding and maintaining **boundaries** to ensure a comfortable work environment, and consistently exhibiting **professionalism** in all your interactions.\n\n**Communication Styles**\n- **Meetings**: Always arrive on time, be prepared to contribute, and listen actively. Respect others' opinions and avoid interrupting. Professionalism is key.\n- **Email Etiquette**: Begin emails with a proper greeting, be concise and clear, and always proofread before sending. Respect your colleagues' time and avoid unnecessary emails.\n\n**Physical/Digital Space**\n- **Cubicle/Desk Space**: Keep your work area tidy and organized. Respect others' personal space and avoid encroaching on their areas. Professionalism includes maintaining cleanliness and order.\n\nBy adhering to these principles, you'll contribute to a positive and productive atmosphere at Global Dynamics. Let's get started!",
      "source": "target",
