      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Welcome to Global Dynamics! As part of your onboarding, we'll be introducing you to our \"Workplace Etiquette 101\" training module. This guide will help you understand the expectations and standards we uphold at our company. Key concepts include demonstrating **respect** for your colleagues and clients, understanding and maintaining **boundaries** to ensure a comfortable work environment, and consistently exhibiting **professionalism** in all your interactions.\n\n**Communication Styles**\n- **Meetings**: Arrive on time, come prepared to contribute, and listen actively. Respect others' viewpoints and avoid interrupting. Professionalism is key.\n- **Email Etiquette**: Use proper greetings, be concise, and proofread before sending. Respect your colleagues' time by being clear and direct.\n\n**Physical/Digital Space**\n- **Cubicle/Desk Space**: Keep your work area organized and clean. Respect others' personal space and avoid encroaching on their areas. Professionalism includes maintaining a tidy and orderly workspace.\n\n**Conflict Resolution**\n- When disagreements arise, address them privately and respectfully. Listen to the other person's perspective and seek a mutually beneficial resolution. Professionalism requires you to handle conflicts calmly and constructively.\n\nBy adhering to these principles, you'll contribute to a positive",
